<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Advtech buys study firm for 2.3 mln rand.</title>
<headline>Advtech buys study firm for 2.3 mln rand.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-12-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>Advanced Technical Systems Ltd (Advtech) said on Thursday it had bought education study aids distributor, Guidelines, for 2.34 million rand with effect from December 1.</p>
<p>Payment will be settled partly in cash and partly by the issue of Advtech &quot;N&quot; shares.</p>
<p>It said the price excluded the liabilities of Guidelines and was subject to adjustment downwards if profit warranties for the three-month period ending February 28, 1997 and 12 month period ending February 28, 1998 were not met.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom 27 11 482 1003</p>
